PART 1871_MIDRANGE PROCUREMENT PROCEDURES



1871.000

Scope of part.



This part prescribes policies and procedures for the acquisition of supplies and services from commercial sources
as a pilot test procurement program.



Subpart 1871.1_General



</TEXT>
