 22.355

Frequency tolerance.


Except as otherwise provided in this part, the carrier frequency of each transmitter in the Public Mobile Services
must be maintained within the tolerances given in Table C-1 of  22.357.


 22.357

Emission types.


Any authorized station in the Public Mobile services may transmit the standard emission types set forth in this section,
regardless of whether they are listed on the station authorization. Before using any emission type(s) other than
those set forth in this section (

