 22.651

470-512 MHz channels for trunked mobile operation.


The following channels are allocated for assignment to transmitters providing trunked public mobile service within
the specified urban areas. All channels have a bandwidth of 20 kHz and are designated by their center frequencies in
MegaHertz.






 22.653

Eligibility.


Only licensees already authorized to provide trunked mobile service or their successors in interest are eligible
to apply for additional use of these channels for trunked mobile service, and then only in the urban areas already authorized.



